¢ Extracting (108;304;404) user-specific information related to the client (1309 from a URI and/or a data storage device (120) connected with the single-point-of-entry server (100); 
¢ Building (401) a user-specific request header according to the user-specific information; 
¢ Transmitting (109;306) the request (130-1) with the user-specific request header to a host (140,150) hosting the web site; 
¢ Receiving a response corresponding to the request (130-1) from the host (140,150) on the single-point-of-entry server (100); 
¢ Performing (111;308-326) reprocessing of the response including at least one modification and/or emulation on the web site according to the request (130-1) at the single-point-of-entry server (100); and 
¢ Transmitting (112;330) a modified response (403) to the client (130).
